org.apache.abdera2.common.lang
Class Lang

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.abdera2.common.lang.SubtagSet
      org.apache.abdera2.common.lang.Lang
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SubtagSet>, Iterable<Subtag>
public final class Lang
extends SubtagSet

Implementation of RFC 4646 Language Tags. Instances are immutable and safe for use by multiple threads. Iterators returned by calling the iterator() method, however, are not threadsafe and should only ever be accessed by a single thread.
